Hermes
======

is a message digesting and distribution system. See 
http://en.opensuse.org/openSUSE:Hermes
for details.

Message can be posted using either the Hermes::Client perl module
directly or via http. HTTP is supported through herminator in 
the herminator directory.

Ask for help in the #opensuse-buildservice channel on freenode.

Klaas Freitag <freitag@suse.de>

